1de/40.png\" class=\"avatar\"\u003e boberfly:\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere‚Äôs also:\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/memononen/nanovg\" data-bbcode=\"true\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"\u003ehttps://github.com/memononen/nanovg\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/memononen/nanosvg\" data-bbcode=\"true\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"\u003ehttps://github.com/memononen/nanosvg\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLooks good.\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":9,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-01-02T01:06:08.721Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":1,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":12,"readers_count":11,"score":2.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":1214,"topic_slug":"can-new-guis-be-created-without-patching","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":54,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":7104,"name":"","username":"christianclavet","avatar_template":"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/c/76d3ee/{size}.png","created_at":"2015-08-07T00:44:35.000Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eHi, Been learning and experimenting on how the interface is done in the URHO editor. I‚Äôm really impressed with all the features there are! Tried The internal GUI is really FAR SUPERIOR of what I‚Äôve experienced with Irrlicht!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHere is a screen. Mostly scaled the icons to be a little bigger. On my monitor the icons looked really tiny. The size I‚Äôve set them is adequate. I found out that the GUI can scale the icons picture without having to scale the image itself. So we could create very high resolutions pictures (for 4k resolution) and simply use a formula to set the desired size. I really find the GUI refresh to be fast!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"spoiler\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://www.clavet.org/files/URHO/EditorTweaks.jpg\" title=\"\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"http://www.clavet.org/files/URHO/EditorTweaks.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"373\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e1920√ó1040\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne part was easy, I had only to load the XML layout definition in the editor itself and edit the GUI, the other part was editing the XML of the SKIN definition for the styles, and the last part was to edit some .AS files because the toolsbars seem to be generated from code.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere 2 things that I was able to use in Irrlicht that is not there: Tabbed windows, and multi-line edit box.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOne thing that would be nice with the editor, is to improve the inspector to have each component in a window (fixed size and collapsable window in a window) that could be put in a single line (title with a direction arrow to expand-collapse). And a content window that take all theses component, so we could use a scrollbar to look at all the component instead of them being squashed and not operable. (This only happen when you have lots of component on a node)\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":10,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-01-02T01:06:21.394Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":13,"readers_count":12,"score":7.6,"yours":false,"topic_id":1214,"topic_slug":"can-new-guis-be-created-without-patching","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"http://www.clavet.org/files/URHO/EditorTweaks.jpg","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"EditorTweaks.jpg","clicks":0}],"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":171,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false}],"stream":[6904,6906,6907,6915,6921,6924,6925,6928,6932,7104]},"timeline_lookup":[[1,2677],[4,2676],[8,2675],[10,2665]],"suggested_topics":[{"id":7304,"title":"Urho3D is crashing on Android 12","fancy_title":"Urho3D is crashing on Android 12","slug":"urho3d-is-crashing-on-android-12","posts_count":1,"reply_count":0,"highest_post_number":1,"image_url":null,"created_at":"2022-07-28T10:03:51.280Z","last_posted_at":"2022-07-28T10:03:51.349Z","bumped":true,"bumped_at":"2022-07-28T10:38:06.014Z","archetype":"regular","unseen":false,"pinned":false,"unpinned":null,"visible":true,"closed":false,"archived":false,"bookmarked":null,"liked":null,"tags_descriptions":{},"like_count":1,"views":126,"category_id":9,"featured_link":null,"has_accepted_answer":false,"posters":[{"extras":"latest single","description":"Original Poster, Most Recent Poster","user":{"id":809,"username":"elix22","name":"","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.u